NOTEÂ Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â  Guidance given in this document can also be applied to specifications for the quality of water required for manual cleaning or disinfection of medical devices (see the ISO 17664 series).
This document does not supersede or modify requirements or test methods of published standards applying to:
