This document specifies the detection of Clostridium (C.)Â perfringens.
This document is applicable to:
â€”Â Â Â Â  products intended for human consumption;
â€”Â Â Â Â  products intended for animal feeding;
â€”Â Â Â Â  environmental samples in the area of food and feed production and handling;
